        <item>
            <title>網民實踐用 ChatGPT 製實體公仔，自創 5 個步驟由生成公仔草圖到 3D 列印</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/chatgpt-figure/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chatgpt-figure</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/chatgpt-figure/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 14 Apr 2025 11:24:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303246</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>生成式 AI 技術席捲創作界，不少網民都用 ChatGPT 來製作吉卜力圖片，有些網民就愛用 GPT 來生成「公仔」。但好多網民都是生成公仔「圖片」來玩玩便算，而近日就有一位網民實踐將 ChatGPT 結合 3D 模型技術，以極為便捷的方法，製作出一系列個人化公仔，不但造型細緻生動，AI、3D 打印的輔助下整個製作流程大幅提速，引起網民熱議。這位網民的例子展示 AI 輔助創作在實體製品上的潛力，實現從構思、繪圖、建模至列印的完整流程。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472116.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472116-681x580.jpg" alt="" width="681" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472116-681x580.jpg 681w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472116.jpg 1057w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 681px" /></a></p><p>這位名為「Model work」的網民在 Facebook 專頁「ChatGPT 4o + Copilot and ALL AI 生成式藝術小小詠唱師」發文，詳細分享其創作過程，強調 GPT 模型強大之處，令公仔設計不再困難，只需簡單五個步驟即可完成 3D 成品。他的創意與執行力，獲得眾多網民讚賞。以下為他的五大關鍵流程解析：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490346772_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490346772_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490346772_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490346772_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p>一、用 ChatGPT 協助生成圖像構想</p><p>他以 ChatGPT 作為起點，輸入想要的角色風格與主題，由 GPT 協助生成角色外觀草圖或描述，作為創作原型。這一步驟大幅減輕繪圖負擔，對無插畫經驗者尤為有用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490420347_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303254 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490420347_1221334695-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490420347_1221334695-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490420347_1221334695.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>二、利用 Tripo3D 將圖像轉化為初步 3D 模型</p><p>接著，他透過 Tripo3D 工具快速將 2D 概念圖轉換成 3D 模型，實現初步的立體化，縮短建模準備時間。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490385309_1221334764.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303255" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490385309_1221334764-518x580.jpg" alt="" width="518" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490385309_1221334764-518x580.jpg 518w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490385309_1221334764.jpg 803w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 518px" /></a></p><p>三、Zbrush 精修與分件，輸出 STL 檔案<br />
為讓模型更具細節與可列印性，他將 Tripo3D 的模型導入專業雕刻工具 Zbrush，進行精修與分件，再輸出 STL 檔案作為 3D 列印的標準格式。</p><p>四、使用赤兔切片軟件進行支撐設置</p><p>STL 檔輸出後，他選用「赤兔」切片軟件（Chitubox 類型工具）進行模型切片與支撐架設，確保列印過程中模型不會變形或倒塌。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490113881_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490113881_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490113881_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490113881_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490063517_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490063517_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490063517_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490063517_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p>五、進行 3D 列印並上色</p><p>最後進行實體列印，他展示多個完成品，包括戴口罩吃泡麵公仔、騎機車角色、戴耳機公仔等，動作與神情極具個性，更成功上色還原插畫風格。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490704421_1221334764.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303258" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490704421_1221334764-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490704421_1221334764-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490704421_1221334764.jpg 720w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490111783_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303259" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490111783_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490111783_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490111783_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490418580_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303260" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490418580_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490418580_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490418580_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p>不少網民看完後紛紛留言讚嘆這套流程「直接把玩具工廠搬進家」，也有人提到「上色先最難，ChatGPT 都幫唔到手」，但亦有留言者回應指出，目前若使用如 Tripo3D、Hi3D、Luma 等進階工具，其實已可生成全綵模型，只要配合全綵 3D 列印機便可省卻手動上色。</p><p>還有網民更直言：「所以可以輕鬆客製化公仔了」，點出這項流程的商業潛力與普及前景。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312-1-694x212.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="212" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312-1-694x212.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312-1.jpg 1232w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312.jpg"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_212.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_212-694x406.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="406" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_212-694x406.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_212.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>透過 AI 結合 3D 技術，這位創作者不僅展示出個人創意，更示範出新一代創作人如何活用科技工具改變傳統創作流程。此例子亦為未來 3D 公仔客製化市場提供極具參考價值的實踐模式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472323.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472323-486x580.jpg" alt="" width="486" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472323-486x580.jpg 486w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472323.jpg 754w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 486px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/592850912909945/search/?q=GPT%20%E5%BE%88%E7%8C%9B%EF%BC%8C">Facebook</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/chatgpt-figure/ai/">網民實踐用 ChatGPT 製實體公仔，自創 5 個步驟由生成公仔草圖到 3D 列印</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
